                            <comment id="16984104" author="jack-lee" created="Thu, 28 Nov 2019 03:03:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mirko24&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mirko24&quot;&gt;mirko24&lt;/a&gt;  When I  append the dependencies as below :&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
			&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.powermock&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
